  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (ML surrogate)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for an ML surrogate model predicting hemolysis index for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the ML model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. The surrogate was trained on CFD-derived shear-stress fields and validated against a held-out test set drawn from the same operating-condition distribution as training. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2).",
  "deviceClass": "Class II",
  "modelRiskLevel": 2,
  "couName": "CPB use",
  "decision": "Accepted",
