      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between the computational and physical domains is not formally assessed at MRL 2. Blood rheology and pump geometry inputs to the CFD solver were taken from published FDA benchmark specifications and are assumed to represent the physical device with sufficient fidelity for this risk level."
