    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The ML surrogate model achieves R² = 0.97 and maximum RH deviation of 8.4 % on the nominal test set, satisfying the ±10 % acceptance criterion. Five-fold cross-validation confirms stable performance across the training distribution. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined COU operating envelope.",
